using For loop Write a program that uses a for loop to print the numbers from 1 to 10.

Using while loop, Write a program that uses a while loop to print the even numbers from 1 to 20.

Write a program that uses a do-while loop to repeatedly prompt the user to enter a number until they enter 100. Display the sum of all the numbers entered.

